{
  "texts": [
    "It is implemented via the BertForSequenceClassification class of the Huggingface Transformers framework (Wolf et al., 2020) and fine-tuned with the regular Trainer class this framework provides.",
    "AdamW (Loshchilov & Hutter, 2019) was used as the optimisation algorithm.",
    "As an input prompt, it is given m sentences to the left and right in addition to the sentence of interest, all separated by [SEP] tokens.",
    "This allowed the model to use signals from surrounding sentences to classify a sentence of interest.",
    "We implemented multiple baseline models combining a tf-idf-encoded bag-of-words feature set with different classification algorithms."
  ]
}